it.uniud.mads.jlibbig.core.std

Class AgentRewritingRule

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.uniud.mads.jlibbig.core.std.RewritingRule
      • it.uniud.mads.jlibbig.core.std.AgentRewritingRule
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ReactionRule<Bigraph>, RewritingRule<Bigraph,Bigraph>

    public class AgentRewritingRule
extends RewritingRule
    This class specialises RewritingRule for ground bigraphs i.e. bigraphs with empty inner interface. Matches are computed by means of AgentMatcher by other matchers can be specified.
    See Also:
